\s INZIRA Y’ABANA B’IMANA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Inzira y’abana b’Imana, nimwe gusa ntihindagurika; n’inzir’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd imwe igoye\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd gutahura, kukw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd imbere y’isezerano\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Hama hari imibabaro yo kuramukwa./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Imibabaro niy’igihe gito, ingorane n’iz’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit igihe gito, har’\bdit*\bdit  Itunga \bdit*\bdit mw’isezerano ry’Uhoraho ribikiw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit abihangana n’abitanga\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.Mwami numpe kwitanga no kwihangana./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yesu Kristo mu kuducungura nawe yaciye mur’iyo nzira; aho yasenga abir’icuya c’amaraso, kubw’imibabaro yar’imbere yiwe\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Yar’imibabaro y’imbere y’agakiza./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Imibabaro niy’igihe gito, ingorane n’iz’ igihe gito, har’ Itunga mw’isezerano ry’Uhoraho ribikiw’ abihangana n’abitanga ./.Mwami numpe kwitanga no kwihangana./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Turanihira mu mitima yacu, dushaka kuva mur’iyi mibabaro; ubutame n’ugucumukura, n’imibabaro yo kuramukwa\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Kukw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd imbere tuzohanagurw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd amarira./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Imibabaro niy’igihe gito, ingorane n’iz’ igihe gito, har’ Itunga mw’isezerano ry’Uhoraho ribikiw’ abihangana n’abitanga ./.Mwami numpe kwitanga no kwihangana./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Twihangane mumitima yacu, intumbero y’Imana ni nziza; kandi ni ku bw’urukund’adukunda, Uhoraho aducisha mu ngorane\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Kugira ngo tube abakristo bashitse./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Imibabaro niy’igihe gito, ingorane n’iz’ igihe gito, har’ Itunga mw’isezerano ry’Uhoraho ribikiw’ abihangana n’abitanga ./.Mwami numpe kwitanga no kwihangana./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umunezero wacu ni wuzure, har’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd imibabaro yo kuramukwa;\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Umwana w’isezerano ari hafi kuvuka, kuko Imana itihana kumpano ./.nt\bd*\bd iyihana no kumuhamagaro wayo./.\bd*
\pc \bdit Imibabaro niy’igihe gito, ingorane n’iz’ igihe gito, har’ Itunga mw’isezerano ry’Uhoraho ribikiw’ abihangana n’abitanga ./.Mwami numpe kwitanga no kwihangana./.\bdit*\bd  \bd*
